  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/ce25fe2be6c495a7fc8b24ecb7edfdc6.poster.avif?t=1774305560\" width=513 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/ce25fe2be6c495a7fc8b24ecb7edfdc6.webm?t=1774305560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/238e9be7ee0b1f3910398522fd9971ac.poster.avif?t=1774305560\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/238e9be7ee0b1f3910398522fd9971ac.webm?t=1774305560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/238e9be7ee0b1f3910398522fd9971ac.mp4?t=1774305560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marooned on a remote island, troop leader Teal finds she has the ability to grow unique seedlings - endangered creatures that love to gather the island's abundant resources. But the seedlings are threatened by greedy gnomes, who also happen to have all the missing parts to the island's only boat…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/8df0fb1067afb07a7aad1d754f9b3007.avif?t=1774305560\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras_big/8df0fb1067afb07a7aad1d754f9b3007.avif?t=1774305560 width=800 height=319 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Collect resources!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your loyal (but not always enthusiastic) troop's different abilities to gather a variety of resources!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/87e89254befe048a777d2eea2a3fd517.avif?t=1774305560\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras_big/87e89254befe048a777d2eea2a3fd517.avif?t=1774305560 width=800 height=375 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Farm and grow!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant and cultivate seeds to repopulate the island with the helpful seedlings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/cd1af2e3c7e511c30b864a6a18d0a2ca.avif?t=1774305560\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras_big/cd1af2e3c7e511c30b864a6a18d0a2ca.avif?t=1774305560 width=800 height=324 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Level up!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed up production, gain new abilities and even automate by leveling up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/9a7359b134485cb727d3d0cbcbc182b3.avif?t=1774305560\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras_big/9a7359b134485cb727d3d0cbcbc182b3.avif?t=1774305560 width=800 height=409 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Fight back!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raise and arm sentry seedlings to defeat the oppressive gnomes and get your sprites back home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/5301824488950563113a5787fc4fe791.avif?t=1774305560\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras_big/5301824488950563113a5787fc4fe791.avif?t=1774305560 width=800 height=278 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Customize!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate to make the island your own! Spruce up your home and island with mix and matchable themed furniture. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/ad6774d513b38e46c1b942033fc68d70.avif?t=1774305560\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras_big/ad6774d513b38e46c1b942033fc68d70.avif?t=1774305560 width=800 height=205 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Befriend!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know your fellow sprites! Chat, give gifts, and fulfill requests to grow your friendships!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fun awaits  on Isle Fae.... see you there!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/a9c1f3a6a1f5ceab451a2c3051d3aec6.poster.avif?t=1774305560\" width=341 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/a9c1f3a6a1f5ceab451a2c3051d3aec6.webm?t=1774305560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> EARLY ACCESS ROADMAP </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2861360/extras/097903ee9b662c0d2873b24c2f3eea0b.avif?t=1774305560\" width=800 height=618 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
